text: Odelzhausen is a town and municipality in Dachau, a district (Landkreis) in Upper Bavaria. The administrative collectivity of Odelzhausen consists of Odelzhausen and the townships of Sulzemoos and Pfaffenhofen an der Glonn. ==Local areas== The municipality of Odelzhausen includes 14 official local areas. *Dietenhausen *Ebertshausen *Essenbach *Gaggers *Hadersried *Höfa *Lukka und Todtenried *Miegersbach *Roßbach *Odelzhausen *St. Johann *Sittenbach *Sixtnitgern *Taxa The following boundaries exist: Ebertshausen, Höfa, Odelzhausen, Sittenbach, Taxa. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:Dachau (district)
